    "description": "The Apollo Jogging Stroller by Delta Children delivers peak performance whether you’re hitting the running trail or strolling the sidewalk. An all-terrain jogger with next level maneuverability, this stroller features a front swivel wheel for 360-degrees of ultra-smooth steering while walking or added stability when locked while actively running. The jogger’s suspension system with visible shock absorbers will smooth out any bumps in the road. Equipped with a water resistant UPF 50+ canopy with peek-a-boo window, adjustable foam handlebar, multi-position reclining seat, swing away child tray, parent organizer with two cup holders and reflective material for nighttime runs, the Apollo is designed to keep parents and kids with an active lifestyle happy. And, when you need to take this jogging stroller with you on a day trip or vacation, it folds easily and has quick-release back wheels that allow for hassle-free storage. Stroller recommended for infants, toddlers and kids up to 50 lbs.Fits the following car seats with the included adapter (car seats sold separately): Graco SnugRide Click Connect 30, 35, 40 Evenflo Nurture Evenflo Embrace. For Britax B-Safe 35 Car Seats, please use the Jogger Car Seat Adapter #‎10040-2294 (sold separately). For Chicco KeyFit 30 Car Seats, please use the Jogger Car Seat Adapter #‎10020-2294 (sold separately).",
